{"id": "art-106", "label": "Art. 106", "title": "Art. 106", "slug": "art-106", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 106 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_352228046\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2352\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_352228046\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)O societate nu poate s&#259; acorde avansuri sau\nîmprumuturi <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> nici s&#259; constituie <span\nclass=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> în vederea subscrierii sau dobândirii\npropriilor sale <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> de c&#259;tre un <span\nclass=SpellE>ter&#355;</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1875242778\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2351\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1875242778\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span> alin. (1) nu\nse aplic&#259; <span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;iilor</span> efectuate în cadrul\n<span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunilor</span> curente ale <span class=SpellE>institu&#355;iilor</span>\nde credit <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ale altor <span class=SpellE>institu&#355;ii</span>\nfinanciare, nici <span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;iilor</span> efectuate în\nvederea dobândirii de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> de c&#259;tre sau\npentru <span class=SpellE>salaria&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\ncu <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;ia</span> ca aceste <span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;ii</span>\ns&#259; nu determine diminuarea activelor nete sub valoarea cumulat&#259; a\ncapitalului social subscris <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a rezervelor care\nnu pot fi distribuite conform <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>\nsau actului constitutiv.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}